{"id":101,"date":"2023-04-28T10:47:25","date_gmt":"2023-04-28T08:47:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.cen-bourgogne.fr\/?page_id=101"},"modified":"2024-02-29T14:50:47","modified_gmt":"2024-02-29T13:50:47","slug":"la-vie-associative","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.cen-bourgogne.fr\/conservatoire-despaces-naturels-de-bourgogne\/la-vie-associative\/","title":{"rendered":"La vie associative"},"content":{"rendered":"<section class=\"cameleon-block cameleon-block-core-spacer\"><div class=\"grid-container\"><div class=\"grid-x grid-padding-x align-center\"><div class=\"cell\">\n<div style=\"height:150px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section>\n\n<section class=\"cameleon-block cameleon-block-core-columns\"><div class=\"grid-container\"><div class=\"grid-x grid-padding-x align-center\"><div class=\"cell\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns width-medium is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group left-padding-s right-padding-s is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-navy-blue-color has-text-color\">Le fonctionnement<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Le Conservatoire d\u2019espaces naturels de Bourgogne est une association de loi 1901. Elle s\u2019appuie sur une <strong>assise citoyenne<\/strong> constitu\u00e9e par les nombreux adh\u00e9rents et b\u00e9n\u00e9voles qui la soutiennent. L\u2019association s\u2019organise autour de trois instances : <strong>le Bureau, le Conseil d\u2019Administration et l\u2019Assembl\u00e9e G\u00e9n\u00e9rale<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"556\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cen-bourgogne.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/CEN-BOURGOGNE-VIE-ASSOCIATIVE-1024x556.jpg\" alt=\"Visite d'un site g\u00e9r\u00e9 par le Conservatoire d'espaces naturels de Bourgogne\" class=\"wp-image-1000\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.cen-bourgogne.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/CEN-BOURGOGNE-VIE-ASSOCIATIVE-1024x556.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.cen-bourgogne.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/CEN-BOURGOGNE-VIE-ASSOCIATIVE-300x163.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.cen-bourgogne.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/CEN-BOURGOGNE-VIE-ASSOCIATIVE-768x417.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.cen-bourgogne.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/CEN-BOURGOGNE-VIE-ASSOCIATIVE.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section>\n\n<section class=\"cameleon-block cameleon-block-core-spacer\"><div class=\"grid-container\"><div class=\"grid-x grid-padding-x align-center\"><div class=\"cell\">\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section>\n\n<section class=\"cameleon-block cameleon-block-core-columns\"><div class=\"grid-container cameleon-contained\"><div class=\"grid-x grid-padding-x align-center\"><div class=\"cell has-background has-mauve-background-color\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns has-mauve-background-color has-background contained width-medium top-padding-s bottom-padding-s is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-navy-blue-color has-text-color\">Le conseil d&rsquo;administration<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u2019association est administr\u00e9e par le <strong>Conseil d\u2019Administration compos\u00e9 de quatre coll\u00e8ges<\/strong> qui g\u00e8re la vie de l\u2019association, pose les orientations et forme l\u2019organe d\u00e9cisionnel. Il se r\u00e9unit trois fois par an.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section>\n\n<section class=\"cameleon-block cameleon-block-core-spacer\"><div class=\"grid-container\"><div class=\"grid-x grid-padding-x align-center\"><div class=\"cell\">\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section>\n\n<section class=\"cameleon-block cameleon-block-core-columns\"><div class=\"grid-container\"><div class=\"grid-x grid-padding-x align-center\"><div class=\"cell\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns width-medium is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-4 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-navy-blue-color has-text-color\">Le Coll\u00e8ge 1<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns width-large is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-3 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group right-padding-xl is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<p>Le Coll\u00e8ge 1 se compose des membres actifs personnes physiques, avec un maximum de douze membres formant le Bureau et ses administrateurs. Les membres de ce coll\u00e8ge ont une voix d\u00e9lib\u00e9rative. La dur\u00e9e des mandats est de trois ans, les membres sortants sont r\u00e9\u00e9ligibles. Ce coll\u00e8ge est \u00e9lu et renouvel\u00e9 par tiers \u00e0 chaque Assembl\u00e9e G\u00e9n\u00e9rale. Le Bureau se r\u00e9unit chaque mois, except\u00e9 en juillet et Ao\u00fbt.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group right-padding-xl is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<ul>\n<li>Pr\u00e9sident : Daniel SIRUGUE<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Vice-Pr\u00e9sident : Patrice NOTTEGHEM<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Secr\u00e9taire g\u00e9n\u00e9rale : R\u00e9gis DESBROSSES<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Secr\u00e9taire adjoint : Francis LABREUCHE<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Tr\u00e9sorier : G\u00e9rard PAYEN<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Tr\u00e9sorier adjoint : Bruno GU\u00c9GAN<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Administrateurs(trices) : Thomas BARRAL, Jean-Michel COUDERC, Alain DESBROSSE et Guy FAVELIER.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section>\n\n<section class=\"cameleon-block cameleon-block-core-spacer\"><div class=\"grid-container\"><div class=\"grid-x grid-padding-x align-center\"><div class=\"cell\">\n<div style=\"height:75px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section>\n\n<section class=\"cameleon-block cameleon-block-core-columns\"><div class=\"grid-container\"><div class=\"grid-x grid-padding-x align-center\"><div class=\"cell\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns width-medium is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-5 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-top is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cen-bourgogne.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/CEN-BOURGOGNE-EQUIPE-DANIEL-SIRUGUE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-983\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.cen-bourgogne.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/CEN-BOURGOGNE-EQUIPE-DANIEL-SIRUGUE.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.cen-bourgogne.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/CEN-BOURGOGNE-EQUIPE-DANIEL-SIRUGUE-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.cen-bourgogne.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/CEN-BOURGOGNE-EQUIPE-DANIEL-SIRUGUE-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-blo